error.message: Declaration of Drupal\aws_connector\Credentials\AWSCredentialProvider::ini($profile = 'default', $filename = NULL) should be compatible with Aws\Credentials\CredentialProvider::ini($profile = NULL, $filename = NULL, array $config = Array)
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to aws_connector.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
